# Course Configuration Panel — Walkthrough

## Problem Found

Three disconnected systems managed courses:

| System | Source | Problem |
|---|---|---|
| [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/BatchManager.tsx#11-16) model | DB (Academic.ts) | No admin CRUD UI |
| [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) | Hardcoded (551 lines) | Requires code deployment to change |
| [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) | Separate DB model | Missing admin page, separate from courses |

## Solution: Unified Program Model

Extended [IProgram](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#17-35) to be single source of truth:

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Program Model<br/>(Academic.ts)"] --> B["Basic: name, code, type, duration"]
    A --> C["Website: shortDescription, image, syllabus, career"]
    A --> D["Pricing: totalFee, paymentType, offer, seatLimit"]
    A --> E["Status: is_active toggle"]
    F["Admin /admin/courses"] -->|CRUD| G["API /api/admin/courses"]
    H["Website"] -->|Read| I["API /api/public/courses"]
    G --> A
    I --> A
```

